### 🛠️ Step 1: Create a Custom Chart

```bash
helm create nginx-demo
cd nginx-demo
```

This creates the following structure:

```bash
nginx-demo/
├── charts/
├── Chart.yaml
├── templates/
│   ├── deployment.yaml
│   ├── _helpers.tpl
│   ├── hpa.yaml
│   ├── ingress.yaml
│   ├── service.yaml
│   ├── configmap.yaml
│   └── tests/
└── values.yaml
```




